Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:02:01.89,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译: 凉菜 Leader  校对: Potianwu  润稿：ATM  时间: 堂堂 AfterFX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one  two  three  four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one  two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:39.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#6  学园祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  马上就要正式表演了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她们会不会已经到了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧一瞧看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超便宜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音好耳熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  您的一份炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪也是来吃炒面的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别急着炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不就要正式演出了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多练习练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦  其实人家也想练习的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果学园祭期间轮到看店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳闸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  又跳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还没炒熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这都第几回了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电炒锅只能同时用三台哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会多用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们班啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成是5班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还挺麻烦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢逛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:36.76,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入场费  一次  50日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式演出前不再练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦  现在走不开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  队伍都排这么长了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能找个人替一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个方案好歹也是我提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能一开始就翘班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  那小紬在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.00,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亲亲爱爱  恶梦馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还不错嘛  没事啦没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  班里的人的话可以随便进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面阴森森的要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小紬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬…你在哪儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你嗓子没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐队练习有点过头而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一次登台亮相对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从三点开始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算这边做完了就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去吧  我会去拜托别人来替的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位小哥不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进  请慢逛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓子还没好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还是有点沙哑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说说看「谢谢您嘞」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谢谢您嘞」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相扑选手相扑选手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把每一次练习当做比赛」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把每一次比赛当作练习」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「相扑不是国技  乃是格斗技」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对优势下被翻盘」  就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推  我推
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推  我推
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了  小澪她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬在这里边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪的话应该在活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点一起去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下就轮到我和小紬休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷窥啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都在练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下你一个人真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按照刚才的感觉来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是被威逼利诱的  不过既然当了轻音部的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想有没有什么我能帮得上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了演出服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还真有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  老师  您的好意小的们心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿着那一身衣服唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要在众目睽睽之下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像这个时机不太对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服大小姐您不中意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我以前穿过的演出服如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想穿刚才那件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop！佐和酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是小澪  换了谁都不会好意思穿这身衣着的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  人家辛辛苦苦做出来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬她们穿得挺开心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们两个！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥又是这种结局…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要给你化个连你自己都认不出来的妆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不劳您大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那各位  正式演出的时候加油咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一搞刚才练的全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才啥事也没发生  啥事也发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到礼堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心哦  因为很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  说起来  小澪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我让澪去做其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主唱  在那么多人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了所以不让她搬器材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
